<!-- ==================== 6. FEATURES ==================== -->
<h2>6. Features Implemented</h2>

<table>
  <tr><th>#</th><th>Feature</th><th>Description</th><th>Status</th></tr>
  <tr><td>1</td><td>Event Creation</td><td>Society heads create events with title, description, date, time, capacity, and venue selection. Events start as PENDING.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>2</td><td>Event Approval</td><td>Admin reviews and approves/rejects pending events before they go live.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>3</td><td>Student Registration</td><td>Students register for published events with server-side capacity enforcement. Duplicate registrations prevented by UNIQUE constraint.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>4</td><td>Student Unregistration</td><td>Students can cancel their registration (status set to CANCELLED). Re-registration supported.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>5</td><td>Attendance Tracking</td><td>Society heads view participant lists and toggle attendance (REGISTERED &harr; ATTENDED) per student.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>6</td><td>Feedback System</td><td>Students who attended an event can submit 1&ndash;5 star rating with comments. One feedback per event per student.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>7</td><td>Event Update Requests</td><td>Society heads request event edits. Admin reviews and applies changes on approval.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>8</td><td>Event Delete Requests</td><td>Society heads request event deletion with a reason. Admin approves or rejects with a reason.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>9</td><td>Notifications</td><td>Society heads see notifications when their requests are approved/rejected, including admin reasons.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>10</td><td>Venue Management</td><td>Admins toggle venue availability. Unavailable venues hidden from event creation forms and rejected server-side.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>11</td><td>Venue Capacity Validation</td><td>Event capacity cannot exceed the selected venue's capacity. Enforced server-side.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>12</td><td>Society Management</td><td>Admins create/delete societies, assign head and co-head roles from existing users.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>13</td><td>Search &amp; Filtering</td><td>Public landing page with real-time search by event title or society name.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>14</td><td>SQL Console</td><td>Built-in admin SQL console with query execution and full database inspector.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>15</td><td>Role-Based Dashboards</td><td>Three distinct dashboards with role-specific features and navigation.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
  <tr><td>16</td><td>Live Countdown</td><td>Event cards show real-time countdown (days, hours, minutes, seconds) to event start.</td><td><span class="badge badge-green">Done</span></td></tr>
</table>

