<!-- ==================== 9. HOW TO RUN ==================== -->
<h2>9. How to Run</h2>

<h3>Local Development (SQLite)</h3>
<pre style="background:#f4f6f9; padding:12px; border-radius:5px; font-size:10pt;">
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm run dev

# Open http://localhost:3000
</pre>

<h3>Production (PostgreSQL)</h3>
<pre style="background:#f4f6f9; padding:12px; border-radius:5px; font-size:10pt;">
# Set environment variable
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@host:port/dbname

# Build and start
npm run build
npm start
</pre>

